   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Setup </uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol> Build </uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol> Develop </uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol> Custom Settings</uicontrol>
               </menucascade> and click <uicontrol>Manage</uicontrol> next to
                  <uicontrol>Power-Adobe</uicontrol> Settings. </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Under the related list section, click <uicontrol>New</uicontrol>. </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Set the <uicontrol>Location</uicontrol> field to Profile and select your desired profile, or User and select the desired User. </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select the <uicontrol>Don't Copy Opportunity</uicontrol> to disallow your desired User/profile from copying the Agreement record to the Opportunity.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>. </p>
